      • setServiceStartTimeWindow

        public CarrierService.Builder setServiceStartTimeWindow(TimeWindow startTimeWindow)
        Sets a time-window for the service.

        Note that the time-window restricts the start-time of the service (i.e. serviceActivity). If one works with hard time-windows (which means that time-windows must be met) than the service is allowed to start between startTimeWindow.getStart() and startTimeWindow.getEnd().

        Parameters:
        startTimeWindow -
        Returns:
